flexible framework,

00:02:16.780 --> 00:02:18.760
and you'll want to
flex it and adapt it

00:02:18.760 --> 00:02:22.450
to your particular
challenge or scenario.

00:02:22.450 --> 00:02:24.760
One of the advantages
of the sprint

00:02:24.760 --> 00:02:28.210
is you can reduce the risks
of downstream mistakes

00:02:28.210 --> 00:02:30.730
by getting to insights
