organizations and consumers

00:03:03.160 --> 00:03:06.370
create something
together, both parties are

00:03:06.370 --> 00:03:09.880
more invested in the outcome.

00:03:09.880 --> 00:03:12.170
So what does this
look like in practice?

00:03:12.170 --> 00:03:14.810
We're going to start by
bringing a team together

00:03:14.810 --> 00:03:19.300
of very different disciplines,
including UX, Eng, PM,

00:03:19.300 --> 00:03:21.080
to create a powerful team.

00:03:21.080 --> 00:03:23.380
We're looking for a
good representation

00:03:23.380 --> 00:03:25.540
of roles and skills.

00:03:25.540 --> 00:03:28.390
And this is going to allow
us to dramatically reduce

00:03:28.390 --> 00:03:31.180
the amount of time that
we spend communicating

00:03:31.180 --> 00:03:36.400
and increase the number of
viable ideas that we generate.

00:03:36.400 --> 00:03:38.590
So once we have
our team together,

00:03:38.590 --> 00:03:41.860
we're going to walk through
the five sprint phases,

00:03:41.860 --> 00:03:47.770
understand, sketch, decide,
prototype, and validate.

00:03:47.770 --> 00:03:51.040
Now, we have a mix of
structured individual work

00:03:51.040 --> 00:03:53.650
and planned group
discussions that

00:03:53.650 --> 00:03:56.410
support a clear
diverge and converge

00:03:56.410 --> 00:03:58.960
process that will
guide the team to get

00:03:58.960 --> 00:04:01.180
on the same page
around the artifacts

00:04:01.180 --> 00:04:04.540
that it's going to produce
to test with the users.

00:04:04.540 --> 00:04:06.310
Now, the ideal design
sprint is going

00:04:06.310 --> 00:04:09.100
to provide time for
team members to reflect

00:04:09.100 --> 00:04:12.790
on the challenge, and also,
opportunities to validate

00:04:12.790 --> 00:04:14.335
or disrupt those ideas.

00:04:16.950 --> 00:04:19.740
So the goal for the first
phase, the understand phase,

00:04:19.740 --> 00:04:23.460
is to gather all of the relevant
data and information at hand.

00:04:23.460 --> 00:04:24.990
We really want to
create a shared

00:04:24.990 --> 00:04:27.510
brain and a line around
a new world together,

00:04:27.510 --> 00:04:30.930
and a new understanding
of the problem space.

00:04:30.930 --> 00:04:33.030
Then, we're going to move
on to the sketch phase.

00:04:33.030 --> 00:04:34.696
And this is when we're
going to generate

00:04:34.696 --> 00:04:38.880
tons and tons of ideas,
tons of potential solutions.

00:04:38.880 --> 00:04:42.150
