00:06:43.870 --> 00:06:46.180
So it can be a
little dispiriting

00:06:46.180 --> 00:06:49.390
that something didn't work,
but it's really useful to know.

00:06:49.390 --> 00:06:53.500
And you've saved all of that
time, money, and resources

00:06:53.500 --> 00:06:55.870
that you might have spent
