in this middle bucket,

00:07:02.500 --> 00:07:04.780
what we called flawed success.

00:07:04.780 --> 00:07:07.290
Some things worked,
some things didn't.

00:07:07.290 --> 00:07:09.010
But you have a path forward.

00:07:09.010 --> 00:07:11.020
You know what you
need to do next.

00:07:11.020 --> 00:07:12.730
And sometimes you
have an epic win.

00:07:12.730 --> 00:07:14.980
Maybe you have a couple
things you want to tweak,

00:07:14.980 --> 00:07:18.080
