your expectations

00:07:20.310 --> 00:07:23.110
with its stakeholders at
the beginning of the sprint

00:07:23.110 --> 00:07:24.910
so that everyone
is aware of this,

00:07:24.910 --> 00:07:27.730
and they know what
the outcomes might be.

