00:08:45.470 --> 00:08:48.260
How can immersion
guide your interaction

00:08:48.260 --> 00:08:51.710
with users, especially users
that you don't know very well?

00:08:51.710 --> 00:08:56.180
I like to think of it
in terms of three steps.

00:08:56.180 --> 00:08:56.980
Step one.

00:08:56.980 --> 00:08:59.560
Immersion is about awareness.

00:08:59.560 --> 00:09:03.220
So first, doing the
background research and study

00:09:03.220 --> 00:09:05.350
that it actually
takes before you

00:09:05.350 --> 00:09:08.590
