environment and users.

00:09:08.590 --> 00:09:11.320
Then, bringing those learnings
with you into these new

00:09:11.320 --> 00:09:13.420
surroundings so that
they can provide you

00:09:13.420 --> 00:09:17.216
the context that you need
to process that correctly.

00:09:17.216 --> 00:09:19.090
And then when you're in
this new environment,

00:09:19.090 --> 00:09:21.040
just being very keenly aware.

00:09:21.040 --> 00:09:25.120
Observing without preconceived
notions, or bias, or judgment.

00:09:25.120 --> 00:09:28.840
So that's awareness.

00:09:28.840 --> 00:09:29.410
