00:09:54.970 --> 00:09:57.280
when you try to listen
to someone speaking,

00:09:57.280 --> 00:10:00.910
it's very easy to let your mind
wander and think about what

00:10:00.910 --> 00:10:02.300
you want to say next.

00:10:02.300 --> 00:10:04.150
