00:10:05.566 --> 00:10:06.770
doing right now, by the way.

00:10:06.770 --> 00:10:10.750
But it's really important
to listen attentively.

00:10:10.750 --> 00:10:12.760
So that's step two.

00:10:12.760 --> 00:10:15.310
And then step three
is taking awareness,

00:10:15.310 --> 00:10:17.746
